curam.util.ctm.bom.impl

Class CodeTableHierarchyReadAndUpsertBOMImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • curam.util.ctm.bom.BusinessObjectModuleImpl
      • curam.util.ctm.bom.impl.CodeTableHierarchyReadAndUpsertBOMImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BusinessObjectModule, ReadAndUpsertBOM

    public class CodeTableHierarchyReadAndUpsertBOMImpl
extends BusinessObjectModuleImpl
implements ReadAndUpsertBOM
    This class is responsible for reading, updating and inserting code table hierarchy BOM information. A Code Table Hierarchy BOM consists of the code table hierarchy record, one or more code table header records and their associated code table item records.

      • convertBusinessObjectContentToXML

        public org.w3c.dom.Document convertBusinessObjectContentToXML(BusinessObjectIdentifier boIdentifier)
                                                       throws AppException,
                                                              InformationalException
        This method takes in a code table hierarchy name as the key for the Code Table Hierarchy BOM, and uses this key to retrieve the code table hierarchy record, and all of the code table header and code table item records associated with this hierarchy. All of this information is then stored in XML format as specified by the BOM infrastructure.
